  "title": "✨ Sales Associate ✨ (Entry Level)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Royal Org</strong><br>\nRoyal Org is a fast-growing outsourced sales and marketing firm specialising in face-to-face marketing and revenue generation. We partner with clients across industries, including NGOs, lifestyle, energy, and FMCG, to boost brand awareness and drive measurable results.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Fast, <em>performance-based</em> career progression</li>\n  <li>Supportive, dynamic, and ambitious team culture</li>\n  <li>Comprehensive training and mentorship from day one</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to develop sales, communication, and leadership skills</li>\n  <li>Team events, recognition programs, and travel opportunities</li>\n  <li>Weekly Payouts</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Represent major brands through in-person marketing campaigns</li>\n  <li>Engage customers and build strong relationships</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with your team to meet targets and grow together</li>\n</ul>\n<p>At Royal Org, we value passion, professionalism, and potential.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you’re driven to learn, grow, and achieve, <strong>apply now</strong> to start your career with us.</p>",
